Leavitt
v.
State 191P16-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 1, 2016

Mr. Owen D. Leavitt, Pro Se.

Ms. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, Mr. Michael D. Waters, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 31st of May 2016 by *440Petitioner to Reconsider Denial of Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of June 2016."
